WEBVTT

00:00.480 --> 00:01.972
<i>My gosh. Did she teach you how to
make this? Previously on sleepy hollow...</i>

00:01.980 --> 00:03.180
Hey.

00:03.210 --> 00:05.010
Move and I will
blow you to hell.

00:05.050 --> 00:06.780
Crane!

00:06.820 --> 00:09.050
I thought bullets didn't work
on the horseman.

00:09.080 --> 00:10.420
He's vulnerable on the stone.

00:10.450 --> 00:11.543
My Tinder date was telling me

00:11.550 --> 00:12.643
about this video
that he watched.

00:12.650 --> 00:16.260
<i>It was posted on Logan MacDonald's
picagram feed.</i>

00:16.290 --> 00:18.120
<i>Somebody hacked his account
and then embedded</i>

00:18.160 --> 00:20.890
the pamphlet's curse
into the video's source code.

00:20.930 --> 00:21.900
Has to be Dreyfuss.

00:21.930 --> 00:23.160
He summoned this creature

00:23.200 --> 00:26.170
<i>and ravaged our noble city
with its pestilence. Why?</i>

00:26.200 --> 00:28.500
I am assembling a team

00:28.540 --> 00:29.770
of my own.

00:29.810 --> 00:31.400
A hero's welcome

00:31.440 --> 00:32.870
to the man of the hour!

00:32.910 --> 00:36.580
Sent the picagram
heard round the world.

00:36.610 --> 00:39.510
I've come to believe
I don't need any of you anymore.

00:39.550 --> 00:43.250
The second recruit is...
Ready to be plucked soon.

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
